@page
@model Bookclub.Pages.FAQModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Frequently Asked Questions ";
    ViewData["FAQAct"] = "active";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>



    <button class="questionToBeAnswered"id="accordian">
    <h2> What happens if I don't read? </h2>
        </button>
    <div class="answerForQuestions">
        <p> That is okay! Not all our members read, it is entirely up to you!</p>
    </div>


<button class="questionToBeAnswered"> 
    <h2> What can I do if the support does not work? </h2>
    </button>
<div class="answerForQuestions">
    <p> It can be tough to find something that wil help; people respond differently.
        Therefore, it is vital to be open about the sort of help you can find in order to fight.</p>
</div>

  <button class="questionToBeAnswered"> 
      <h2> Is this book club open to anyone?  </h2>
      </button>
    <div class="answerForQuestions">
        <p> Yes, any adult or elderly person is free to join. The books read and chosen are chosen based within that age range</p>
    </div>
    
    
    <button class="questionToBeAnswered"> 
      <h2> Is there a monthly fee? </h2>
      </button>
    <div class="answerForQuestions">
        <p> No, this book club is free to join and free to cancel!</p>
    </div>

    <button class="questionToBeAnswered"> 
      <h2> Where can I go in case I need further support with mental health </h2>
      </button>
    <div class="answerForQuestions">
    <p> Depending on the cirumstances of your needs, call 999 or find a healthcare near you based on this link: <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/service-search/mental-health/find-an-urgent-mental-health-helpline" target="_blank">here</a></p>
    </div>

    <button class="questionToBeAnswered"> 
      <h2>How do I get in touch with Between 2 Lines </h2>
      </button>
    <div class="answerForQuestions">
    <p>   You can contact us by visting this page and sending us your request here: <a asp-page="/Contact">Contact Us</a>  </p>
    </div>



